quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  36,55,"Inna as-haba aljannati alyawmafee shughulin fakihoon"
  36,56,"Hum waazwajuhum fee thilalinAAala al-ara-iki muttaki-oon"
  36,57,"Lahum feeha fakihatun walahumma yaddaAAoon"
  36,58,"Salamun qawlan min rabbin raheem"
  36,59,"Wamtazoo alyawma ayyuhaalmujrimoon"
  36,60,"Alam aAAhad ilaykum ya banee adamaan la taAAbudoo ashshaytana innahu lakumAAaduwwun mubeen"
  36,61,"Waani oAAbudoonee hatha siratunmustaqeem"
  36,62,"Walaqad adalla minkum jibillankatheeran afalam takoonoo taAAqiloon"
  36,63,"Hathihi jahannamu allatee kuntumtooAAadoon"
  36,64,"Islawha alyawma bimakuntum takfuroon"
  36,65,"Alyawma nakhtimu AAala afwahihimwatukallimuna aydeehim watashhadu arjuluhum bima kanooyaksiboon"
  36,66,"Walaw nashao latamasnaAAala aAAyunihim fastabaqoo assiratafaanna yubsiroon"
  36,67,"Walaw nashao lamasakhnahumAAala makanatihim fama istataAAoo mudiyyanwala yarjiAAoon"
  36,68,"Waman nuAAammirhu nunakkis-hu fee alkhalqiafala yaAAqiloon"
  36,69,"Wama AAallamnahu ashshiAArawama yanbaghee lahu in huwa illa thikrunwaqur-anun mubeen"
  36,70,"Liyunthira man kana hayyanwayahiqqa alqawlu AAala alkafireen"
